{"4152120": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "天下功夫出少女", "steam_appid": 4152120, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲概述】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是落魄邪派雲雨寨的唯一繼承人，正打算賣掉門派財產前往現代大都市過上幸福生活時，一位身份神秘的功夫少女真蘭忽然來踢館，破壞了你離開武林的退休計劃。但在陰差陽錯之下，你發現門派傳承下來、被武林唾棄的「純陽金童寶典」竟然真的可以透過做色色的事情來讓女性變強？！於是你與真蘭訂下了30天內助她成為武林霸主的約定......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在30天內，你可以選擇好好鍛煉♂真蘭，專心讓她成為最強；可以選擇主動拉近與真蘭的關係，用你的愛打動她；可以選擇深入♀了解性格各異的三大門派館主、拯救因某種原因而飽受折磨的她們，與她們結下不解之緣。但是，請記得時間有限。如果你沒有做好準備，當那道帶有殺氣的身影出現在眼前，一切都已經來不及......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲特色】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/extras/5aec21d1e2b67c4f3f45203ca7f0d400.poster.avif?t=1776198397\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/extras/5aec21d1e2b67c4f3f45203ca7f0d400.webm?t=1776198397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/extras/5aec21d1e2b67c4f3f45203ca7f0d400.mp4?t=1776198397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/extras/36847d08fb82faa2c0b6c4a703f25904.poster.avif?t=1776198397\" width=1170 height=654 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/extras/36847d08fb82faa2c0b6c4a703f25904.webm?t=1776198397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/extras/36847d08fb82faa2c0b6c4a703f25904.mp4?t=1776198397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"