 playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/extras/657f02e4dd081ccda23912ef1b5401df.poster.avif?t=1776198397\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/extras/657f02e4dd081ccda23912ef1b5401df.webm?t=1776198397\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/extras/657f02e4dd081ccda23912ef1b5401df.mp4?t=1776198397\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>名稱：蓮華</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>所屬門派：鐵家山莊</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鐵家山莊的掌門，擅長使用摔跤的天才格鬥家。雖然擁有健壯的肌肉與驚人的怪力，但個性非常膽小、陰沉內向，為自己的外觀感到自卑，害怕與他人交談，特別是極少與男性溝通。不懂愛情是怎麼一回事、卻一直很憧憬戀愛和婚姻，原本想說一邊鍛煉一邊尋找最強的男人當伴侶，但不知不覺間自己就變得太強了所以很苦惱。不過誰也不知道的是，在她陰沉的外表之下竟然還有那樣的另一面......</p>", "short_description": "在風起雲湧的江湖武林中，作為落魄邪派「雲雨寨」繼承人的你，意外與初出茅廬的功夫少女真蘭結成同盟、並要在30天內讓她成為武林霸主！而令她變強的秘訣，竟然就是雲雨寨代代相傳的男女雙修色情練功法？！三大門派的女館主也在等著你的挑戰......用你的功力與精力震撼武林吧。", "supported_languages": "繁體中文, 英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文, 韓文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/3ecfbe0f1af55a03544603831e012b4d2cfff475/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1776198397", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/6649b0eb4ce302f815637509cb520e59a23ad7d6/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776198397", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4152120/6649b0eb4ce302f815637509cb520e59a23ad7d6/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776198397", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows7/8/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 560 / AMD Radeon HD 6870  DirectX 版本: 11<br></li><li><str